**Engine.** New CLI: `bim-ai trace --image <path> [--brief <path>] [--archetype-hint <key>] -o layout.json`. Runs SKB-04 + SKB-14 + SKB-07 (deterministic) + polygon recovery + optional OCR. Output: `(StructuredLayout, advisories)`. Registered as a tool descriptor per API-V3-01. The brief is passed through as metadata only ‚Äî the deterministic CV does not interpret it; agents that read the brief do their own thing with it.
